data.description: Welcome to your dream oasis! Nestled on an expansive .97-acre lot, this newly listed property offers everything you've been searching for in a home.     The main residence boasts a comfortable and spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom layout, including a separate stand-up shower.     Step outside and discover your own private paradise. The beautiful backyard is fully fenced, providing a safe and secure space for your family and pets to enjoy. The crown jewel of this outdoor haven is the marcite in-ground pool, perfect for those hot summer days. You'll love spending time on the screened-in back porch/patio, where you can relax and entertain with ease, all while taking in the picturesque views of your lush surroundings.    But that's not all a this property also features a separate mother-in-law suite, complete with 1 bedroom and 1 bathroom. Whether you need extra space for guests, a home office, or a cozy retreat, this suite offers endless possibilities.    The generous yard offers ample room for children to play, pets to roam, and family gatherings to flourish. It's a place where memories are made and cherished for years to come. Privacy is paramount here, with plenty of space between you and your neighbors, creating a serene and tranquil atmosphere.    Don't miss this incredible opportunity to own a slice of paradise. This listing won't last long, so schedule a showing today and start living the life you've always dreamed of. Welcome home!
